<h2>About the Service</h2>
<p>
Can I Afford It? applies well established personal finance best practices to your current
financial circumstances and thereby helps you in making your decisions on any purchases.
</p>
<p>
The more data you provide, the more accurate the results will be.
However, it is still meant to be only a sanity check and not decisive by any stretch.
</p>
<p>
We acknowledge that individual judgments may vary and hence we allow our community members
to voice their opinions as well.
We hope this will provide a well-rounded response to the question posed.
</p>
